SELECT TIMESTAMPDIFF(4,CHAR(CURRENT TIMESTAMP - MAX(TSTAMP_ACTUAL))) AS TTR FROM CARD.HEADER WHERE PART_CODE = ' & #PART_CODE#$ & "' AND SPROD_ACTUAL IN ('0280','0230') AND LINEA = 'CARD' AND DECPROD = 'P' AND TIMESTAMPDIFF(4,CHAR(TSTAMP_ACTUAL - TSTAMP_INICIO)) < 172800

WITH MI_TABLA AS(SELECT TSTAMP_ACTUAL AS FECHA_PRODUCCION FROM CARD.HEADER WHERE PART_CODE = ' & #PART_CODE#$ & "' AND SPROD_ACTUAL IN ('0280','0230') AND LINEA = 'CARD' AND DECPROD = 'P' AND TIMESTAMPDIFF(4,CHAR(TSTAMP_ACTUAL - TSTAMP_INICIO)) < 172800 UNION ALL SELECT (TSTAMP_INICIO + 3 Month)AS FECHA_PRODUCCION FROM CARD.HEADER WHERE PART_CODE = '" & #PART_CODE#$ & "' AND SPROD_ACTUAL IN ('0280','0230') AND LINEA = 'CARD' AND DECPROD = 'P' AND TIMESTAMPDIFF(4,CHAR(TSTAMP_ACTUAL - TSTAMP_INICIO)) > 172800) SELECT TIMESTAMPDIFF(4,CHAR(CURRENT TIMESTAMP - MAX(FECHA_PRODUCCION))) AS TTR FROM MI_TABLA

WITH MITABLA (NIVEL,ETIQUETA,COMP_SN) AS (SELECT 1,RAIZ.ETIQUETA,RAIZ.COMP_SN  FROM CARD.SN_BLINDCHECK RAIZ WHERE RAIZ.ETIQUETA = ' & SERIAL_CELESTICA$ & "' AND STATUS='OK' UNION ALL SELECT PADRE.NIVEL+1, HIJA.ETIQUETA, HIJA.COMP_SN  FROM MITABLA PADRE, CARD.SN_BLINDCHECK HIJA WHERE PADRE.COMP_SN = HIJA.ETIQUETA AND PADRE.NIVEL < 10 AND STATUS='OK') SELECT PART_CODE, REF_DES AS SN_HIJO_CLIENTE, COMP_PN AS PN_CELESTICA from CARD.CIQSSFC WHERE ETIQUETA IN (SELECT COMP_SN AS SN_HIJO FROM MITABLA) AND SPROD IN ('B110','B300')  AND STATUS = 'M' AND TRIM(REF_DES) <> ''
